of crimson wine group ltd increased the number of directors constituting the board from six to seven and appointed francesca schuler to be a director of the company filling the vacancy to hold office until the next annual meeting of stockholders the board has determined that ms schuler is independent under the listing standards of the nasdaq stock market at the time of her appointment the board did not appoint ms schuler to any committee of the board ms schuler has over  years of experience leading and managing multichannel businesses and has focused on brand strategy portfolio management product development and innovation ecommerce and digital strategy crm and sales ms schuler is currently the chief marketing officer at inshape health clubs crimson wine group ltd elimination of natasha hayes as vice president of marketing feb   effective on february   as a result of a management restructuring of crimson wine group ltd the position of vice president of marketing has been eliminated and as a result natasha hayes is no longer an employee of the company similar private companies by industry company name region  brewing co llc united states  way brewing company inc united states  karat wines llc united states  brix llc united states  stars brewing company united states recent private companies transactions typedate target buyback march    request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does not create or control the content for inquiries please contact sp global market intelligence directly by clicking here stock quotes market data is delayed at least  minutes company lookup most searched private companies company name geographic region lawyers committee for civil rights under law united states nyc inc united states the advertising council inc united states bertelsmann ag europe rush university united states sponsored financial commentaries sponsored